				<li><a href="#tc">Tropical Cyclones (Hurricanes) and Tropical Storms </a></li>
			    <li><a href="#lks">Local "Kona" Storms ("Sub-Tropical" Cyclones)</a></li>
			    <li><a href="#fs">Frontal Systems</a></li>
				<li><a href="#ull">Upper Level Lows</a></li>
				<li><a href="#etss">Extra-Tropical Storm Surf</a></li>
